  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upstream Ante: Unleash Your Strategy in a High-Stakes Card Game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the thrilling world of Upstream Ante, a roguelike card game inspired by Poker and Texas Hold’em. Strategize, place your bets, and play with powerful hands to outwit your opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940560/extras/a8cee2912bf297f23d8ca7873d4d843a.poster.avif?t=1729909036\" width=578 height=195 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940560/extras/a8cee2912bf297f23d8ca7873d4d843a.webm?t=1729909036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the art of combining standard cards with jokers, buffs, and debuffs to create winning strategies. Earn chips, unlock more jokes, and drive your enemy to bankruptcy to ramp up the intensity. With every hand, the stakes get higher, and the game gets more chaotic. Can you reach intensity level 15 and claim victory?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940560/extras/315871207580d9213c6bec53fd3af488.poster.avif?t=1729909036\" width=655 height=195 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940560/extras/315871207580d9213c6bec53fd3af488.webm?t=1729909036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A challenging yet rewarding roguelike experience with multiple winning strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Endless possibilities with every upgrade, debuff, discard, angel card, devil card, and joker dramatically altering your game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Over 70 unique Jokers and 16 unique Upgrades and Debuffs to add a twist to each hand.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax with our Jazz-infused Lo-fi soundtrack, and let the rhythm guide your strategy. Unwind, go with the flow, and immerse yourself in the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940560/extras/5249a83097f716d96829c4fd9605c31c.poster.avif?t=1729909036\" width=457 height=193 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940560/extras/5249a83097f716d96829c4fd9605c31c.webm?t=1729909036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 8 different game modes, each offering a unique gameplay experience. Find the mode that suits your style and play your way to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940560/extras/b1350d35146d88a3b8dca4950f744d3e.poster.avif?t=1729909036\" width=387 height=193 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940560/extras/b1350d35146d88a3b8dca4950f744d3e.webm?t=1729909036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upstream Ante: Unleash Your Strategy in a High-Stakes Card Game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the thrilling world of Upstream Ante, a roguelike card game inspired by Poker and Texas Hold’em. Strategize, place your bets, and play with powerful hands to outwit your opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940560/extras/a8cee2912bf297f23d8ca7873d4d843a.poster.avif?t=1729909036\" width=578 height=195 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940560/extras/a8cee2912bf297f23d8ca7873d4d843a.webm?t=1729909036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the art of combining standard cards with jokers, buffs, and debuffs to create winning strategies. Earn chips, unlock more jokes, and drive your enemy to bankruptcy to ramp up the intensity. With every hand, the stakes get higher, and the game gets more chaotic. Can you reach intensity level 15 and claim victory?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940560/extras/315871207580d9213c6bec53fd3af488.poster.avif?t=1729909036\" width=655 height=195 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940560/extras/315871207580d9213c6bec53fd3af488.webm?t=1729909036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A challenging yet rewarding roguelike experience with multiple winning strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Endless possibilities with every upgrade, debuff, discard, angel card, devil card, and joker dramatically altering your game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Over 70 unique Jokers and 16 unique Upgrades and Debuffs to add a twist to each hand.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax with our Jazz-infused Lo-fi soundtrack, and let the rhythm guide your strategy. Unwind, go with the flow, and immerse yourself in the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940560/extras/5249a83097f716d96829c4fd9605c31c.poster.avif?t=1729909036\" width=457 height=193 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940560/extras/5249a83097f716d96829c4fd9605c31c.webm?t=1729909036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 8 different game modes, each offering a unique gameplay experience. Find the mode that suits your style and play your way to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940560/extras/b1350d35146d88a3b8dca4950f744d3e.poster.avif?t=1729909036\" width=387 height=193 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940560/extras/b1350d35146d88a3b8dca4950f744d3e.webm?t=1729909036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
